para_trans: Regarding administrative approval for leasing out a private building for this institution.
Department of Medical Education and Pharmaceuticals
Government Correctional Certificate No: IBhade-0624 / P.No.251 / Administration-2
New Mantralaya, Lokmanya Tilak Marg, Mumbai-400001
1) Government Decision, Medical Education and Pharmaceuticals Department No: IBhade-0624 / Q. No.251 / Administration-2, dated 10.02.2026

The Government decision dated 10.02.2026 in respect of the above mentioned issue is vide Issue No. "The said private building for the said college is being approved to be made available on lease for a period of next 03 years from the date of this Government decision or as per the requirement of the college till such time as the Government building becomes available or until further orders. Accordingly, the Dean, Government Medical College, Hingoli, should enter into a lease agreement as required at the institute level. "

"Post facto approval is being granted for leasing out of the said private building for the said college for a period of next 03 years from the date 01.07.2025 or until further orders as per the requirement of the college unless a government building is available.
Accordingly, the Dean, Government Medical College, Hingoli entered into a lease agreement at the institute level.
This government certificate is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
